  "settings_info_pulse_launcher_feature_home": "Music-first home screen with Now Playing, artwork, and volume / playback controls right from the lock screen",
  "settings_info_pulse_launcher_feature_library": "Quick access to albums, artists, playlists and podcasts — with a cover wall and large, finger-friendly controls",
  "settings_info_pulse_launcher_feature_dap": "DAP Sync compatibility: plays the folder layout (Music/Podcasts) synced by Aurora Pulse natively — including from SD card",
