  "settings_info_pulse_launcher_feature_widgets": "Customizable widgets, Vibe themes and wallpapers for portrait and landscape — ideal for DAPs with horizontal displays",
  "settings_info_pulse_launcher_feature_focus": "Focus mode: no noisy app drawer, just a curated set of audio apps and shortcuts",
